=======================
Django EDU Installation
=======================

Thanks for downloading Django EDU

Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~

* At least python 2.3 installed, http://www.python.org/
* A resent revision of Django project installed, http://www.djangoproject.com/

Install
~~~~~~~

To install, run the following command inside this directory:

    python setup.py install

Manual Install
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Or if you'd prefer, you can simply place the included ``django-edu`` directory
somewhere on your PYTHONPATH, or symlink to it from somewhere on your
PYTHONPATH; this is useful if you're working from a Subversion checkout.

Further Reading
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you want or need a more verbose set of instructions please refer to the 
documentation in docs/index.txt 